<section id="Section542567">
    <title>
      <anchor id="Anchor549030" role="Index" xreflabel="customers:by customer type"/> 
      <indexterm significance="normal">
        <primary>customers</primary>

        <secondary>by customer type</secondary>
      </indexterm>Customers by Customer Type</title>

    <para id="Para543188">To view Customers by Customer Type, select the
    "Customers by Customer Type" option from the "Displays" menu. The
    following screen will appear:</para>

    <para id="Para542573">
      <screenshot>
        <mediaobject>
            <imageobject>
               <imagedata fileref="images/SO_Disp_custByCustType.png" id="Graphic542927"/>
            </imageobject>

            <caption id="Caption542907">Customers by Customer Type</caption>
        </mediaobject>
      </screenshot>
   </para>

    <para id="Para543180">When displaying Customers by Customer Type, you are
    presented with the following options:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para574340">All Customer Types</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x196a388">
            <para>Select to display Customers for all Customer Types.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para543113">Selected</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x196a3d0">
            <para>Specify Customer Type whose Customers you want to
          display.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para543115">Pattern</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x196a418">
            <para>Enter a Customer Type pattern to select a range of Customer
          Types.</para>

            <para id="Para656122">Refine your search using Regular Expressions,
          as described in <link endterm="Anchor77806" id="XRef656121" linkend="Anchor77806"> Pattern Matching with Regular
          Expressions</link>"Topic: Pattern Matching with Regular
          Expressions".</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para554929">Show Inactive Customers</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x196a460">
            <para>Select to show inactive Customers in the display.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para543011">Customers</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x196a4a8">
            <para>Display lists Customers for specified Customer Type(s).</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

    <para id="Para543013">To the far right of the screen, the following
    buttons are available:</para>

    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para543014">CLOSE</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x196a514">
            <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
          desktop.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para574939">QUERY</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x196a55c">
            <para>Select to generate the display, using the specified
          parameters.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>

      <varlistentry>
        <term id="Para653748">PRINT</term>

        <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x196a5a4">
            <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>

